spanGrp.span: Jina la baba yangu ni Gidamsangu
I grew up with the mulbadaw dance
Nikakulia kwenye ngoma aina ya mulbadaw
Often I dance the mulbadaw dance
Later they came to marry me
gwajiilay abi hij hay aa matabigd ar quwaar gaftaad ab hiji
I gave birth at this time, I couldn't go home, I stayed here
Nikazaa hapo sasa mpaka nikashindwa kwenda nyumbani nikaa hapo
heet hay aa qawuuy siid haw
ar agweegw qoday mooda qahaqw eemeedeeny
I dance the mulbadaw a lot
Mimi ni wa binti wa Gidansangw
My things are finished, I'm leading my people
